45:32.146 --> 45:34.814
So, Mr. Andretti,
your first time on the freeway?

45:35.023 --> 45:37.024
It's Webber. Adam Webber.

45:37.192 --> 45:40.027
Mind if I change the station?
Better traffic reports on a.m.

45:40.195 --> 45:41.654
