45:49.121 --> 45:51.831
Go back, you had him. Go back, go back.

45:52.040 --> 45:55.376
- Back, back.
- Okay, okay.

45:55.544 --> 45:58.087
- That's it.
- There.

46:01.550 --> 46:04.719
